]] || [[NBC]]\n|-\n| 1970 || ''[[The Virginian (TV series)|The Virginian]]'' || Stephanie White || \"[[List of The Virginian episodes|Nightmare]]\" || [[Robert Gist]] || [[NBC]]\n|-\n| 1970 || ''[[The Tim Conway Show (1970 TV series)|The Tim Conway Show]]'' || Herself (cameo) || \"To Cuba with Love\" || [[Alan Rafkin]] ||[[CBS]]\n|-\n| 1970 || ''[[Journey to the Unknown (film)|Journey to the Unknown]]''<ref name=\"ReferenceB\">TV movie culled from the series ''Journey to the Unknown''</ref> || Hostess || [made-for-TV movie] || [[Michael Lindsay-Hogg]], [[Don Chaffey]] || [[broadcast syndication|Syndication]]\n|-\n| 1970 || ''[[The Tim Conway Comedy Hour]]'' || Herself (guest star) || \"Episode #1.3\" || Bill Hobin || [[CBS]]\n|-\n| 1971 || ''[[Journey to the Unknown|Journey to Murder]]''<ref name=\"ReferenceB\">TV movie culled from the series ''Journey to the Unknown''</ref> || Hostess || [made-for-TV movie] || [[Gerry O'Hara]], John Gibson || [[broadcast syndication|Syndication]]\n|-\n| 1972 || ''[[The Sixth Sense (TV series)|The Sixth Sense]]'' || Joan Fairchild || \"[[The_Sixth_Sense_(TV_series)#Season_2:_1972|Dear Joan: We're Going to Scare You to Death]]\" || [[John Newland]] || [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]\n|-\n| 1975 || ''[[Easter Island]]'' || Narrator (voice) || [made-for-TV documentary] || [[Jos\u00e9 G\u00f3mez-Sicre]] || [[PBS]]\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Award !! Category !! Title / Honor !! Result\n|-\n| 1945 || [[National Board of Review|National Board of Review Awards]] || [[National Board of Review Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]] || ''[[Mildred Pierce (film)|Mildred Pierce]]'' || {{won}}\n|-\n| 1946 || [[Academy Awards]] || [[Academy Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]] || ''Mildred Pierce'' || {{won}}\n|-\n| 1946 || [[New York Film Critics Circle|New York Film Critics Circle Awards]] || [[New York Film Critics Circle Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]] || ''Mildred Pierce'' ||